{"tid":1454500,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"HV7400車主Chiu Chi Wai盗竊大肚婆車牌","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:26:22.000Z","uid":41067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac215f731abfb250f70d9df8bda55b77234665b0","tid":1454500,"uid":41067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"代友post:<br />\n<br />\n此車(HV7400)車主因為星期五26/7/2019泊車阻人(在貨櫃碼頭南路， <br />\n介乎ATL 與 二號貨櫃碼貨之間的迴旋處 ，附近一個沒街名的停車位置)阻住了其他車主，<br />\n打了電話通知他，落到嚟又唔肯倒車，HV7400車主唔肯倒車之餘仲要發爛渣，拆除/盜竊了受影響者大肚婆的車牌，<br />\n當時大肚婆不在埸，要靠其他車主告知，<br />\n又因為佗住8個月身紀又行動不便，令到一位大肚婆收工都要週圍走去其他車房整番個全新嘅車牌。<br />\n當晚致電HV7400車主，佢唔認係佢拆車牌，然後到29/7/2019星期一先打番嚟道歉, 毫無悔意。<br />\n以下奉上他的罪証及車牌。相信HV7400車主在一間叫YAMATO LOGISTICS (HK) LTD 番工，佢電話係91925048<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D7oytNF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD7oytNF.jpg&h=ae088e57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izLdtNG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizLdtNG.jpg&h=e850f75b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rm5kTem.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frm5kTem.jpg&h=05fa7ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNmoQ02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNmoQ02.jpg&h=fa802f16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3G3uMzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3G3uMzo.jpg&h=a9372f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnb8hF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftnb8hF3.jpg&h=60526c31&s={SIZE}\" />。"},{"pid":"2018f1742218319541094546b548801edd6e2235","tid":1454500,"uid":1621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"唔係太睇得明，7400唔係泊得好地地咩？反而架TT頂住哂其他車？"},{"pid":"bd8484fa1557276ea35e21a0375ee49ba98b6f7b","tid":1454500,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"